arts.ttl: Salford up to third after brushing aside Harrogate to claim fifth successive win
arts.sum: Cole Stockton and Matty Lund struck for the visitors at Harrogate.

Harrogate's 1-1 draw with Fleetwood on Sunday ended five straight defeats. Salford's 1-0 win over Morecambe and their fourth straight victory fired them into the playoffs for the first time this seas...
